=== Features II ===

{| style="font-size: 85%; text-align: center;" class="wikitable sortable"
|-
! BitTorrent client
! [[Cache]]<ref name="cache">Reduces disk usage, file fragmentation (in case it is not preallocated) and latencies due to larger written blocks and cached data for hash checking finished pieces.</ref>
! [[Webseeding|Web seeding]]<ref name="webseed">Recently implemented (unofficial) web seeding feature, see [http://www.bittornado.com/docs/webseed-spec.txt HTTP-Based Seeding Specification]</ref>
! [[Broadcatching]] ([[RSS]])
! Prioritization
! Selective downloads
! [[SOCKS]]
! Tracker exchange <ref name="tex">http://www.bittorrent.org/beps/bep_0028.html</ref>
! Remote control via web
! [[BitTorrent (protocol)#Indexing|Search Engine]]
! Auto updates
! Notes
! Video Streaming (linear stream)
